data.description: Lake view! Assumable VA loan with restrictions meaning the buyer has to qualify but has a fixed low rate 3.75%! Captivating Pristine Front Porch Mystique home square footage is 2186 under air (according to builder but verify) on a lake located in the prestigious Del Webb Tradition, 55+ active community. 3/2/2 +Den, open floor plan for wonderful entertaining. Three bedroom/Den, gourmet kitchen, upgraded laundry room, elegant finishes, screened porch q/ lake view. Come and live the Florida dream.  The community boasts a fabulous clubhouse with resort pool and lots of activities. Tradition is the up and coming area on the Treasure Coast. ALERT This home has an assumable VA loan with restrictions meaning the buyer has to qualify but has a fixed low rate 3.75% so call the agent for details. ALERT
